<A>__{charlie, richard and the old men behold peggy, bobbing and dipping playfully in the sky. we begin to hear charlie's voice singing "peggy sue" o.s. peggy looks down with wonder at the earth, and then like a comet, soars into the blackness. in an instant she becomes a star.}
