<A>__{hospital room day moving from two to c.u. peggy, fragments of the reunion, the cake coming towards her, fragments of words in echo effect: 'your heart stopped for a while..." father's voice: 'you're a very lucky young lady...' doctor: 'a (explain) of the head...' mom's voice: 'but you're going to be all right now, the paramedics got there...' mom, 'we were so worried..." echoing of, until once voice is left. charlie. sitting opposite her bed, as he has been every minute of her illness. he looks wan and old, worried sick, but trying to sing 'peggy sue' for her.}
